{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"76d3c3aadc","title":"挽蔡和森、蔡畅母葛太夫人联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"41cb1a30ec","index":0,"year":1943,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"76d3c3aadc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"95de447af6","type":"paragraph","text":"挽蔡和森、蔡畅母葛太夫人联","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"76d3c3aadc"},{"id":"b0dc3c3b62","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年）老妇人：新妇道","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"76d3c3aadc"},{"id":"fb9e97b9d8","type":"paragraph","text":"儿英烈，女英雄。[1]基健豪太夫人是幕和森、蔡畅的母亲，向警予的婆婆。蔡和森（1895-1931），湖南湘乡永丰（今属双峰县）人。早年在湖南省立第一范学校与毛泽东同学，并一起发起组织新民学会。1919年赴法国勤工检学，1921年回国。曾任中共中央宜传部部长、中央政治局委员。1931年在广州领驻。蔡畅（1900-1990），潮南湘乡永丰（今属双峰县）人。蔡和森之妹，新民学会会员，1919年赴法国工径学，1922年加入中国社会主义青年团，1923年转入中国共产党。1924年赴莫斯科东方大学学习，1925年同国。曾任中共中央妇女运动委员会书记、全国妇联主席、全国人大常委会副委员长等职。1990年9月在北京道世。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"76d3c3aadc"}],"page":{"id":"2f76d6995a","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"76d3c3aadc","start":285,"end":285}}}},"__N_SSG":true}